ActMotor Vehicle Safety Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS (TRANSMISSION CONTROL FUNCTIONS) which modify vehicle starting requirements to accommodate new technologies (i.e., gasoline-electricity hybrid vehicles) and introduce mandatory requirements for a brake shift interlock for vehicles with an automatic transmission and a clutch ignition interlock for vehicles with a manual transmission.
